<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Accounts Dashboard</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.16/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/accounts.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="my-navbar">
        <div class="user-profile">
            <img id="user-pfp" src="../images/pfp_final_1.png" alt="user-pfp">
            <div class="user-name">Amogha Khare</div>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-center-section">
            <div>Accounts Dashboard</div>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-icons">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-bell nav-icon"></i>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="navbar-mobile">
        <div class="exam-name">Accounts Dashboard</div>
    </div>

    <div class="thought-section">
        <div class="thought-box">"Financial wisdom begins with understanding your educational investment."</div>
    </div>

   <div class="main-section">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
            <img src="../images/bank.png" alt="payment img">
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">Fee Payment</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
            <img src="../images/due-date.png" alt="dues img">
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">Pending Dues</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
            <img src="../images/online-learning.png" alt="course fee img">
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">Current Course Fee</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
            <img src="../images/due-date.png" alt="due date img">
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">Next Fee Due</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
            <img src="../images/payment.png" alt="receipt img">
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">Payment History</div>
    </div>
   </div>

   <footer class="bg-gray-200 text-gray-600 py-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-wrap justify-center text-center">
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/4 mb-4 sm:mb-0 px-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">Financial Support</h3>
        <p class="text-sm">Need help with payment options?</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 text-sm">Contact Finance Office</a>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/4 mb-4 sm:mb-0 px-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">Quick Links</h3>
        <ul class="list-none text-sm">
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600">Dashboard</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600">Accounts</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600">Support</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/4 mb-4 sm:mb-0 px-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">Contact Finance</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          Finance Department<br>
          Nrutyashree Dance Academy<br>
          BT Kawade Road, Pune<br>
          Phone: +91 9822155819
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full sm:w-1/4 mb-4 sm:mb-0 px-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">Follow Us</h3>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600 mx-2">
            <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600 mx-2">
            <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600 mx-2">
            <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-600 mx-2">
            <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-300 py-4 mt-6">
      <div class="container mx-auto text-center text-gray-500 text-sm">
        &copy; 2008 Nrutyashree Dance Academy. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>